MobileAEC
public static final class MobileAEC.AggressiveMode
extends java.lang.Object

For security reason, this class supports constant aggressiveness of the AECM instance in MILD, MEDIUM, HIGH, AGGRESSIVE, MOST_AGGRESSIVE.
